 <body style="text-align: center">
  <p>
    <img src='img/icon.png' width="120px" height="120px">
  </p>
  <p>
    <h3>Whoa, a bash shell inside Slack!</h3>
    <small>creates a rudimentary file system in every channel</small>
  </p>
  <p id='messages' />
